casebody.data:
FEDERAL TREASURY ENTERPRISE SOJUZPLODOIMPORT, et al., petitioners,
v.
SPI SPIRITS LIMITED, et al. No. 13-685. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014. Case below, 726 F.3d 62 .

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice SOTOMAYOR took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
